  "description": "<h3><strong>Position: Operator</strong></h3><p>Location: 2 bus stops away from Joo Koon MRT<br />with in-house canteen<br />Working hours: 6:45am to 6:45pm (AM Shift only)<br />Designated pick up points provided<br /></p><p><u><strong>Summary of Job:</strong></u></p><p>Operating the unloading machine.<br /></p><p><u><strong>Duties and Responsibilities:</strong></u></p><p>~  Packing of finished goods.</p><p>~  Cleaning of workstation.</p><p>~  Other activities as and when required as assigned<br />~  if required, Operate the unloading stacker</p><p><u><strong>Job Requirements:</strong></u></p><p>~ willing to work from 6:45am to 6:45pm (Mon to Thurs)<br />~ able to work Overtime as and when required<br />~ Physically Fit - require to arrange items and put together neatly and standing is required for most of the time.<br />~ On the Job Training provided</p>",
